        "authorId" : "6eca0ade-9879-4dd7-ad14-547e16f5c041",
        "body" : "I agree with @jsafrane that it should not be a Kubernetes decision point what storage driver is used for Docker.\n",
        "createdAt" : "2015-10-13T19:32:25Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2015-10-29T11:24:36Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "6eca0ade-9879-4dd7-ad14-547e16f5c041",
        "tags" : [
