        "authorId" : "6eca0ade-9879-4dd7-ad14-547e16f5c041",
        "body" : "that said, it seems like coupling e2e_opts to the storage driver is a little too subtle.\n\ncan we just have a separate flag in salt that controls devicemapper only?  then have a config-e2e.sh that uses that option if required?\n",
